\lim_{x \to \infty}\frac{a_nx^n+\cdots+a_0}{b_mx^m+\cdots+b_0}=\frac{a_n}{b_m}.
\frac{a_nx^n+\cdots+a_0}{b_mx^m+\cdots+b_0}=\frac{x^n}{x^m}\cdot\frac{a_n+\cdots+\frac{a_0}{x^n}}{b_m+\cdots+\frac{b_0}{x^m}}.
\lim_{x \to \infty}\frac{a_n+\cdots+\frac{a_0}{x^n}}{b_m+\cdots+\frac{b_0}{x^m}} =\frac{\lim_{x \to \infty}a_n+\cdots+\frac{a_0}{x^n}}{\lim_{x \to \infty}b_m+\cdots+\frac{b_0}{x^m}}=\frac{a_n}{b_m}.
